  "_comment": "IDEAL preset — high-frequency paper bot with paper leverage. Target ~2-3 trades / 2 min. Real margin ~$500 simulated via ~3-5x effective leverage (notional > equity). 2 tick-scalpers (sub-second) + 5 minute-bar strats (regime-diversified) + alpha research collection + funding scanner.",
